# Keep renv's dependency scanner out of the equivalence harness. The generators use
# real reference libraries (pracma, numpy, …) that are AUTHORING-TIME tools living in
# the gitignored equivalence/env/, not course dependencies. Without this, renv would
# report the project "out-of-sync" for pracma and a stray renv::snapshot() could add
# it to renv.lock, which must stay render-infrastructure only.
equivalence/
